title: Dunfermline North and Rosyth by-elections: Make sure you can have your say! (Fife Council)
text: ( Source : Fife Council ) IF you live in the Dunfermline North or Rosyth council wards make sure you're registered to vote so you can have your say in the Local Government by-elections on 26 November . The by-elections are taking place
